    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the limits but i phrased it as staying ahead of the pain because once it hits i cant even move. if i dose it more frequently and keep the levels steady in my blood wouldn't that be better than waiting for it to flare up and then trying to fix it? like, isn't it better to prevent the peak pain than chase it?",
